    "Management": {
      "text": "Treat underlying disease\nO2\nif\nHypoxemia\nPerform\nthoracentesis\nvs.\nchest tube\nif evidence of respiratory distress\nMay need Video-Assisted Thoracic surgery (VATS)\nAntibiotics\nPiperacillin-tazobactam\n3.375-4.5gm q6hr IV or\nimipenem\n0.5-1gm q6hr\nConsider adding\nvancomycin\nif patient at risk for\nMRSA",
